{
  "message": "release: bump published crates to 0.2.1 for rider metadata\n\nSummary:\n\n- Increments all crates published on crates.io from 0.2.0 to 0.2.1.\n\n- Keeps dependency constraints unchanged (still compatible at ^0.2.0) to minimize release risk while republishing rider-bearing crate metadata.\n\nValidation:\n\n- cargo check --workspace --all-targets was attempted; publishable crates compile, but workspace check still fails in non-publish test target due pre-existing `screen_snapshots.rs` arity mismatch unrelated to this version bump.",
